OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774271469
OL,3,CPilot and co-pilot dead after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into fire engine at New York
OL,5,Cairport
OL,7,FA pilot and co-pilot have died after a
OL,8,Fplane crashed into a fire engine on a
OL,9,Frunway at New York's LaGuardia
OL,10,FAirport, according to ITV News' US
OL,11,Fpartner CNN.
OL,13,FAround 11.40pm local time on Sunday
OL,14,F(4.40am GMT), the Air Canada jet hit
OL,15,Fthe vehicle, which had been responding
OL,16,Fto a separate incident, crushing the
OL,17,Ffront nose of the plane, authorities
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
