PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774271469
OL,3,CPilot and co-pilot dead after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into fire engine at New York
OL,5,Cairport
OL,7,FTwo people inside the fire and rescue
OL,8,Ftruck were injured in the crash, a law
OL,9,Fofficial told CNN.
OL,11,FThere were 72 passengers and four crew
OL,12,Fmembers aboard the Jazz Aviation
OL,13,Fflight operating on behalf of Air
OL,14,FCanada, according to a statement from
OL,15,Fthe airline, however it said these
OL,16,Fnumbers are "subject to confirmation".
OL,18,FThe airport has been closed while
OL,19,Finvestigations take place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
