OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774271469
OL,3,CPilot and co-pilot dead after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into fire engine at New York
OL,5,Cairport
OL,7,F"At approximately 11:40 p.m. on
OL,8,FSunday, a Jazz Aviation flight
OL,9,Foperating on behalf of Air Canada was
OL,10,Finvolved in an incident on Runway 4 at
OL,11,FLaGuardia Airport in which the
OL,12,Faircraft struck a Port Authority
OL,13,FAircraft Rescue and Firefighting
OL,14,Fvehicle that was responding to a
OL,15,Fseparate incident," the Port Authority
OL,16,Fof New York and New Jersey said in a
OL,17,Fstatement.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
