OL,3,CPilot and co-pilot dead after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into fire engine at New York
OL,5,Cairport
OL,7,FThe flight had set off from Montreal-
OL,8,FPierre Elliott Trudeau International
OL,9,FAirport, the major airport serving
OL,10,FMontreal, just over an hour before the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FThe plane was going about 130 miles
OL,14,Fper hour just before it hit the fire
OL,15,Ftruck, according to the last data
OL,16,Fpoint collected before the collision
OL,17,Fby Flightradar24.
OL,26,@oD@brr
