OL,3,CPilot and co-pilot dead after plane
OL,4,Ccrashes into fire engine at New York
OL,5,Cairport
OL,7,FMultiple videos taken by bystanders
OL,8,Fand posted on social media showed the
OL,9,Fjet with severe damage to the front of
OL,10,Fthe aircraft.
OL,12,FPictures show the severely damaged Air
OL,13,FCanada plane illuminated by
OL,14,Ffloodlights and emergency vehicles
OL,15,Fparked nearby on the runway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
